---
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
import MyEducation from "../components/my-education.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="About Me"
      description="Hello 👋 I'm a Data Analyst | Data Engineer living in Brisbane. I have a profound passion for data analysis and visualisation, consistently driven to uncover hidden patterns through expert coding and analytical skills."
    />

    <img src="/assets/images/about.png" class="relative z-30 w-full my-10 rounded-xl" />
    <!--Bio -->
    <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Short Bio</h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      Data analysis 📊, data engineering ⚙️, back-end development 👩🏻‍💻.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Education</h2>
    <MyEducation />
    <!--Skills -->
    <h2
      class="mt-5 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold lg:mt-10 sm:mt-6 dark:text-neutral-200"
    >
      Skills
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      <ul class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg">
        <li>Programming languages: Python, R, Java.</li>
        <li>Data analytics: SQL, Power BI, Numpy, Pandas, Jupyter Notebooks, Dash.</li>
        <li>Data engineering: PySpark, ETL Pipeline</li>
        <li>Backend development: Python FastAPI, Flask</li>
        <li>Database: Postgres, MySQL, Oracle, Snowflake.</li>
        <li>Cloud: Microsoft Azure</li>
        <li>Version control: Git.</li>
        <li>Soft skills: Time Management, Teamwork, Problem solving, Documentation, Engaging Presentation, Decision making, interpersonal skills.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold lg:mt-10 sm:mt-6 dark:text-neutral-200">Let's Connect</h2>
    <!--Contact -->
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
     Check out my <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rosa-pham-63b332243/" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 underline">LinkedIn</a> and <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/dinhlang86" class="text-indigo-600 underline">GitHub</a> here, or you can send me an <a href="mailto:dinhlang86@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline"
        >email</a
      > and I'll be sure to get back to you.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
